# UI Components

## Component Library
This project uses a custom UI component library based on shadcn/ui:
- Button, Input, Select and other form controls
- Tabs, Dialog, Popover for navigation and modals
- Card, Badge for display elements
- Toast for notifications

## Component Usage Pattern
- UI components are imported from `./ui/` directory
- Components follow a consistent styling pattern
- Most components accept standard HTML attributes plus custom props
- Dark mode support is built into components

## Key UI Components
- Tabs: Used for view switching (month/week in calendar)
- Cards: Container for widget contents
- Badges: Used for status indicators and tags
- Buttons: Various sizes and styles for actions
